1. *Nazvao* sam joj da proverim kako je. (I called her to check on her.)
2. Ona mi je *nazvala* pre nego što je otišla. (She called me before she left.)
3. *Nazvaću* je sutra da se raspitam za njenu putovanje. (I'll call her tomorrow to inquire about her trip.)
4. On je *nazvan* učenikom meseca. (He was called student of the month.)
5. *Nazvaće* se ovaj most novim imenom. (This bridge will be called the new name.)